k\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 01, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104epv1719810593542.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/epv1719810593542.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/epv1719810593542.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cbs1665702603412\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $totkeys\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"cbs1665702603412___totkeys_292615\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the total number of keys for an entity.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"cbs1665702603412__topic_d90230e1_d90231e1_d90232e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cbs1665702603412__p_d90233e1_d90234e1_d90235e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totkeys</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cbs1665702603412__topic_d60067e1_d60068e1_d60069e1_d60070e1_d60071e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1177459e75\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9821e1_d9822e1_d9823e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9821e1_d9822e1_d9823e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Parameter</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9821e1_d9822e1_d9823e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Data Type</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9821e1_d9822e1_d9823e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9821e1_d9822e1_d9823e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9821e1_d9822e1_d9823e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">String</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9821e1_d9822e1_d9823e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cbs1665702603412__topic_d60072e1_d60073e1_d60074e1_d60075e1_d60076e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1177459e147\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9824e1_d9825e1_d9826e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totkeys</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9824e1_d9825e1_d9826e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9824e1_d9825e1_d9826e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Meaning</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9824e1_d9825e1_d9826e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\"\"</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9824e1_d9825e1_d9826e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">An error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9824e1_d9825e1_d9826e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">&gt;=1</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9824e1_d9825e1_d9826e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Total number of primary keys, candidate keys, and indexes.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9827e1_d9828e1_d9829e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totkeys</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9827e1_d9828e1_d9829e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9827e1_d9828e1_d9829e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Error constant</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9827e1_d9828e1_d9829e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Meaning</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9827e1_d9828e1_d9829e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">-1102</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9827e1_d9828e1_d9829e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">&lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt;</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cbs1665702603412__table_d9827e1_d9828e1_d9829e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cbs1665702603412__topic_d60077e1_d60078e1_d60079e1_d60080e1_d60081e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1177459e292\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cbs1665702603412__p_d90245e1_d90246e1_d90247e1\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cbs1665702603412__section_hx3_htk_xbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1177459e302\">Example: Validating Keys in Batch Mode</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example uses the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totkeys</span> function to\n               validate primary and candidate keys in batch mode:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"cbs1665702603412__pre_gbh_3tk_xbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$KEYNBR$ = 1\n$MAXKEYS$ = $totkeys\nwhile ($KEYNBR$ &lt; $MAXKEYS$)\n if ($keytype($entname, $KEYNBR$) = \"P\" | $keytype($entname, $KEYNBR$) = \"C\")\n validatekey $entname, $KEYNBR$\n endif\n $KEYNBR$ = $KEYNBR + 1\nendwhile\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrk1665702576500.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Validate</a><p>Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jwi1665702576586.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validatefield</a><p>Validate a field of the current occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fdp1665702576817.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validatekey</a><p>Validate a key of the current occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bwv1665702576896.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validateocc</a><p>Validate an occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jqe1665702576424.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$dataerrorcontext</a><p>Return the context of the last validation error.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dmp1665702603557.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$keyfields</a><p>Return a list of the fields that make up a primary or candidate key or index.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nij1665702601782.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$keymod</a><p>Return a value indicating whether the specified key has been modified.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/upd1665702601935.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$keytype</a><p>Return the type of the specified key.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wcw1719485700746.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$keyvalidation</a><p>Identify whether a primary or candidate key requires validation.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7420454\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7420454\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$totkeys Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 01, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $totkeys Return the total number of keys for an entity. $totkeys { ( Entity ) } Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used. Return Values Table 2. Values returned in $totkeys Value Meaning \"\" An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. >=1 Total number of primary keys, candidate keys, and indexes. Table 3. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $totkeys Value Error constant Meaning -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component. Use Allowed in all component types. Example: Validating Keys in Batch Mode The following example uses the $totkeys function to validate primary and candidate keys in batch mode: $KEYNBR$ = 1 $MAXKEYS$ = $totkeys while ($KEYNBR$ < $MAXKEYS$) if ($keytype($entname, $KEYNBR$) = \"P\" | $keytype($entname, $KEYNBR$) = \"C\") validatekey $entname, $KEYNBR$ endif $KEYNBR$ = $KEYNBR + 1 endwhile Copy Related Links Validate Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default). validatefield Validate a field of the current occurrence. validatekey Validate a key of the current occurrence. validateocc Validate an occurrence. $dataerrorcontext Return the context of the last validation error. $keyfields Return a list of the fields that make up a primary or candidate key or index. $keymod Return a value indicating whether the specified key has been modified. $keytype Return the type of the specified key. $keyvalidation Identify whether a primary or candidate key requires validation. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}